Niger state governor, Abubakar Sani Bello delivered the Alkali Mustapha polling unit in Kontagora local government area of the state for the All Progressives Congress (APC). Below are the results of the PU: Presidential APC 397 PDP 32  Senate APC 253 PDP 83  House of Representatives APC 287 PDP 34 Defection report part of PDP propaganda — Niger APC No more opposition in Kontagora — Gov Bello Niger gov loses supporters in own town